Give me the car key.

82
00:07:20,210 --> 00:07:22,430
I'll sleep in the car.

83
00:07:22,430 --> 00:07:26,170
Hey, I didn't get to tell you how brightly you...

84
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:29,370
shone...

85
00:07:29,370 --> 00:07:31,620
It'll be pretty when they bloom.

86
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:34,090
Obviously.

87
00:07:34,090 --> 00:07:35,890
Don't you want to know the
meaning behind the flower?

88
00:07:35,890 --> 00:07:37,750
No, I don't.

89
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:39,260
A heart for my long-lost friend-

90
00:07:39,260 --> 00:07:41,120
Shut up if you don't want to get buried.

91
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,750
I'm tired.

92
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:44,340
You brought me all the way here.

93
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:47,290
