95
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:56,330
I don't think I would've let it
slide with anyone else.

96
00:07:57,400 --> 00:08:02,200
His back was pretty warm...

97
00:08:20,970 --> 00:08:23,130
What a nightmare.

98
00:08:40,290 --> 00:08:42,690
Yikes. It's a thief.

99
00:08:42,690 --> 00:08:47,660
