going to the flower market today.

100
00:09:00,170 --> 00:09:01,730
So, if you avoid me now,

101
00:09:01,730 --> 00:09:04,460
will you have a different grade in the evening?

102
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:05,820
Hand me your report card.

103
00:09:05,820 --> 00:09:08,630
It just feels different.

104
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:26,520
 

105
