- Why are you reading that out loud?
- No one's listening. So what?

107
00:09:33,650 --> 00:09:37,000
Exactly. No one's listening, so why?

108
00:09:40,290 --> 00:09:42,500
I see.

109
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:43,900
Here.

110
00:09:46,810 --> 00:09:48,790
Why did you ask me for the report card

111
