185
00:14:33,730 --> 00:14:35,490
Hey!

186
00:14:35,490 --> 00:14:37,370
You can't unspeak what's already been said.

187
00:14:37,370 --> 00:14:39,520
I'd get sick before you do.

188
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:43,400
Gosh, I'm aching all over.

189
00:14:45,290 --> 00:14:47,500
Don't you feel like you're wasting your prime?

190
00:14:47,500 --> 00:14:51,660
Going from book shop, library, flower
shop, book shop, library, flower shop...

191
00:14:51,660 --> 00:14:54,580
You're not that much older than me.

192
00:14:57,640 --> 00:14:59,680
- Ma'am.
- Yeah?

193
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:02,130
Can I go on a date here?

194
00:15:02,130 --> 00:15:04,920
Please go hang out outside!

195
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:08,080
Trying to bring in a freeloader...

196
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:09,700
With whom?

197
00:15:10,700 --> 00:15:12,430
Someone I like.

198
00:15:16,300 --> 00:15:19,230
I hope it goes well!

199
00:15:22,310 --> 00:15:24,420
You don't need to come in on your hospital days.

200
00:15:24,420 --> 00:15:27,370
Aigoo. Don't treat me like a patient.

201
00:15:27,370 --> 00:15:30,290
Look at you throw a tantrum.
You're alive and well.

202
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:34,010
Hyung.

203
00:15:34,010 --> 00:15:37,220
What do you think about a guy
who goes in for a kiss suddenly?

204
00:15:37,220 --> 00:15:38,870
Is he cute?

205
00:15:41,210 --> 00:15:43,430
You see my face every day.

206
00:15:43,430 --> 00:15:45,430
Gosh, seriously.

207
00:15:48,830 --> 00:15:50,670
Wait a second. W-What? What?

208
00:15:50,670 --> 00:15:53,460
Are you dating that class president?

209
00:15:53,460 --> 00:15:55,600
No. Dating, my foot.

210
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:57,070
No?

211
00:15:57,070 --> 00:15:58,870
Wow, you trash.

212
00:15:58,870 --> 00:16:02,070
I've never seen you ask such a frivolous question.

213
00:16:02,070 --> 00:16:04,570
- Geez...
- Bring her in here officially next time.

214
00:16:04,570 --> 00:16:06,440
I need to study her carefully.

215
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,990
Who are you to study her?

216
00:16:07,990 --> 00:16:10,580
You don't even know how to read people.

217
00:16:10,580 --> 00:16:12,490
Without me, you'd be...

218
00:16:12,490 --> 00:16:16,100
I want to decide whether to give
her free drinks or not until I'm 70.

219
00:16:16,100 --> 00:16:18,590
Oh, yes. Of course.

220
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:23,610
You usually get sensitive during your check-ups.

221
00:16:23,610 --> 00:16:25,500
I'm glad you seem better lately.

222
00:16:25,500 --> 00:16:27,330
I am sensitive.

223
00:16:27,330 --> 00:16:30,250
If she says yes, I need to plan our dates.

224
00:16:31,090 --> 00:16:34,020
