01:10:26,090 --> 01:10:31,690
 ♫ Come closer ♫ 

1058
01:10:31,690 --> 01:10:38,690
 ♫ The red sunset ♫ 

1059
01:10:38,690 --> 01:10:45,560
 ♫ Night and day meet briefly ♫ 

1060
01:10:45,560 --> 01:10:51,850
 ♫ Like us back then ♫ 

1061
01:10:53,950 --> 01:10:59,570
 ♫ Like falling asleep ♫ 

1062
01:10:59,570 --> 01:11:08,680
 ♫ Pretending not to know and embrace ♫ 

1063
01:11:08,680 --> 01:11:15,610
 ♫ It's like love that gets pushed away ♫ 

1064
01:11:15,610 --> 01:11:22,640
 ♫ Like the longing that comes back ♫ 

